Class Ref

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.agenarisk.api.Ref

  • public final class Ref
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a reference dictionary for XML, JSON and relevant values for objects in AgenaRisk API v2 The notes below map these terms with the corresponding features of AgenaRisk Desktop
